Installation

1. Make "MantisStats" folder in "plugins" folder of your MantisBT installation.
2. Unpack content of the downloaded archive into the created "MantisStats" 
folder.
3. In your MantisBT's Web interface go to "Manage" -> "Manage Plugins" and 
click on "Install" for "MantisStats" plugin.


Upgrade

1. Unpack content of the downloaded archive into the existing "MantisStats" 
folder (if unsure - see above) overwriting files.
2. Check if database "upgrade" is needed on the "Manage Plugins" page.
